name: Mama Cat
description: Street Cats of Vis is a project I founded on the island of Vis, in Croatia. Mama Cat is one of the cats I feed on my terrace, and the most territorial cat I’ve ever known. All the cats we monitor are spayed or neutered and have regular food, water and shelter. If you'd like to support this project, you can make a donation at streetcatsofvis.com (mention HEN if you do!)
